Package org.nerd4j.csv.field.converter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCSVFieldConverter<S,T>
    Abstract implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that performs the expected behavior and modifies the CSVFieldProcessContext accordingly with the framework execution policy.
    BooleanToString
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Booleans into Strings.
    DateToString
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Dates into Strings.
    EmptyCSVFieldConverter<V>
    Represents an empty converter that doesn't perform any real conversion, it returns the given object.
    EnumToString<E extends Enum<E>>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Enums into Strings.
    NumberToString<N extends Number>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Numbers into Strings.
    StringToBoolean
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Strings into Booleans.
    StringToDate
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Strings into Dates.
    StringToEnum<E extends Enum<E>>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Strings into Enums.
    StringToNumber<N extends Number>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Strings into Numbers.
